{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775862397146,"sessionID":"ses_2865b0a75ffepxYCm60X9v5r8p","part":{"id":"prt_d79a5ac65001AtaGq2ET7TEce5","messageID":"msg_d79a59b73001qkXcQejFxViqA2","sessionID":"ses_2865b0a75ffepxYCm60X9v5r8p","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/go.mod"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/go.mod</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: module github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n2: \n3: go 1.23.0\n4: \n5: require (\n6: \tgithub.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 v5.2.1\n7: \tgithub.com/prometheus/client_golang v1.19.1\n8: \tgolang.org/x/net v0.35.0\n9: \tk8s.io/api v0.32.0\n10: \tk8s.io/apimachinery v0.32.0\n11: \tk8s.io/client-go v0.32.0\n12: \tk8s.io/klog/v2 v2.130.1\n13: \tsigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.19.0\n14: )\n15: \n16: require (\n17: \tgithub.com/beorn7/perks v1.0.1 // indirect\n18: \tgithub.com/cespare/xxhash/v2 v2.3.0 // indirect\n19: \tgithub.com/davecgh/go-spew v1.1.2-0.20180830191138-d8f796af33cc // indirect\n20: \tgithub.com/emicklei/go-restful/v3 v3.11.0 // indirect\n21: \tgithub.com/evanphx/json-patch/v5 v5.9.0 // indirect\n22: \tgithub.com/fxamacker/cbor/v2 v2.7.0 // indirect\n23: \tgithub.com/go-logr/logr v1.4.2 // indirect\n24: \tgithub.com/go-openapi/jsonpointer v0.21.0 // indirect\n25: \tgithub.com/go-openapi/jsonreference v0.20.2 // indirect\n26: \tgithub.com/go-openapi/swag v0.23.0 // indirect\n27: \tgithub.com/gogo/protobuf v1.3.2 // indirect\n28: \tgithub.com/golang/protobuf v1.5.4 // indirect\n29: \tgithub.com/google/gnostic-models v0.6.8 // indirect\n30: \tgithub.com/google/go-cmp v0.7.0 // indirect\n31: \tgithub.com/google/gofuzz v1.2.0 // indirect\n32: \tgithub.com/google/uuid v1.6.0 // indirect\n33: \tgithub.com/josharian/intern v1.0.0 // indirect\n34: \tgithub.com/json-iterator/go v1.1.12 // indirect\n35: \tgithub.com/mailru/easyjson v0.7.7 // indirect\n36: \tgithub.com/modern-go/concurrent v0.0.0-20180306012644-bacd9c7ef1dd // indirect\n37: \tgithub.com/modern-go/reflect2 v1.0.2 // indirect\n38: \tgithub.com/munnerz/goautoneg v0.0.0-20191010083416-a7dc8b61c822 // indirect\n39: \tgithub.com/pkg/errors v0.9.1 // indirect\n40: \tgithub.com/prometheus/client_model v0.6.1 // indirect\n41: \tgithub.com/prometheus/common v0.55.0 // indirect\n42: \tgithub.com/prometheus/procfs v0.15.1 // indirect\n43: \tgithub.com/x448/float16 v0.8.4 // indirect\n44: \tgolang.org/x/oauth2 v0.23.0 // indirect\n45: \tgolang.org/x/sys v0.30.0 // indirect\n46: \tgolang.org/x/term v0.29.0 // indirect\n47: \tgolang.org/x/text v0.22.0 // indirect\n48: \tgolang.org/x/time v0.7.0 // indirect\n49: \tgoogle.golang.org/protobuf v1.35.1 // indirect\n50: \tgopkg.in/evanphx/json-patch.v4 v4.12.0 // indirect\n51: \tgopkg.in/inf.v0 v0.9.1 // indirect\n52: \tgopkg.in/yaml.v3 v3.0.1 // indirect\n53: \tk8s.io/kube-openapi v0.0.0-20241105132330-32ad38e42d3f // indirect\n54: \tk8s.io/utils v0.0.0-20241104100929-3ea5e8cea738 // indirect\n55: \tsigs.k8s.io/json v0.0.0-20241010143419-9aa6b5e7a4b3 // indirect\n56: \tsigs.k8s.io/structured-merge-diff/v4 v4.4.2 // indirect\n57: \tsigs.k8s.io/yaml v1.4.0 // indirect\n58: )\n\n(End of file - total 58 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"module github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n\ngo 1.23.0\n\nrequire (\n\tgithub.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 v5.2.1\n\tgithub.com/prometheus/client_golang v1.19.1\n\tgolang.org/x/net v0.35.0\n\tk8s.io/api v0.32.0\n\tk8s.io/apimachinery v0.32.0\n\tk8s.io/client-go v0.32.0\n\tk8s.io/klog/v2 v2.130.1\n\tsigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.19.0\n)\n\nrequire (\n\tgithub.com/beorn7/perks v1.0.1 // indirect\n\tgithub.com/cespare/xxhash/v2 v2.3.0 // indirect\n\tgithub.com/davecgh/go-spew v1.1.2-0.20180830191138-d8f796af33cc // indirect\n\tgithub.com/emicklei/go-restful/v3 v3.11.0 // indirect","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":