{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775862583195,"sessionID":"ses_2865b0a75ffepxYCm60X9v5r8p","part":{"id":"prt_d79a88a3e0013iPzOsLN5dwBac","messageID":"msg_d79a87dd7001S64m0BfYO5CSjN","sessionID":"ses_2865b0a75ffepxYCm60X9v5r8p","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:18","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-011/design.md","offset":400,"limit":150},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-011/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n400: <base64-encoded PKIX data>\n401: -----END PUBLIC KEY-----\n402: ```\n403: \n404: ### Kubernetes Secret Structure\n405: \n406: ```yaml\n407: apiVersion: v1\n408: kind: Secret\n409: metadata:\n410:   name: picod-router-identity\n411:   namespace: <AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE>\n412:   labels:\n413:     app: agentcube\n414:     component: router\n415: type: Opaque\n416: data:\n417:   private.pem: <base64-encoded PKCS#1 PEM>\n418:   public.pem: <base64-encoded PKIX PEM>\n419: ```\n420: \n421: ### Algorithm: RS256\n422: \n423: - **Signing**: RSA private key + SHA-256 hash\n424: - **Verification**: RSA public key + SHA-256 hash\n425: - **Key format**: PKCS#1 for private, PKIX for public\n426: - **Token format**: JWS Compact Serialization (header.payload.signature)\n427: \n428: ---\n429: \n430: ## Security Considerations\n431: \n432: ### Key Management\n433: \n434: 1. **Private Key Protection**: Private key never leaves the Router pod or K8s Secret\n435: 2. **Public Key Distribution**: Public key can be safely distributed to sandbox pods\n436: 3. **Secret Access**: Requires RBAC permission to create/get Secrets in target namespace\n437: 4. **Ephemeral Fallback**: Non-cluster environments use ephemeral keys (logged warning)\n438: \n439: ### Token Security\n440: \n441: 1. **Short-lived tokens**: 5-minute expiration limits exposure window\n442: 2. **Unique signatures**: RS256 ensures tokens cannot be forged without private key\n443: 3. **Session binding**: session_id claim ties token to specific session\n444: 4. **No refresh tokens**: Short expiration, session-level lifecycle management\n445: \n446: ### RBAC Requirements\n447: \n448: ```yaml\n449: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n450: kind: Role\n451: metadata:\n452:   name: agentcube-router-jwt\n453: rules:\n454: - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n455:   resources: [\"secrets\"]\n456:   verbs: [\"create\", \"get\"]\n457:   resourceNames: [\"picod-router-identity\"]\n458: ```\n459: \n460: ---\n461: \n462: ## Migration Notes\n463: \n464: ### Adding JWT Support\n465: \n466: 1. **New dependency**: Already included in go.mod (`github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5`)\n467: 2. **RBAC setup**: Ensure Router has Secret create/get permissions\n468: 3. **Namespace configuration**: Set `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` for non-default namespace\n469: 4. **Key rotation**: Delete `picod-router-identity` Secret to trigger new key generation\n470: \n471: ### Downstream Changes\n472: \n473: - Sandbox pods must validate JWT using public key from Secret\n474: - Public key can be mounted as volume from Secret or fetched via K8s API\n475: \n476: ---\n477: \n478: ## File Index\n479: \n480: | Path | Purpose |\n481: |------|---------|\n482: | `pkg/router/jwt.go` | JWTManager implementation with key generation, token signing, and secret storage |\n483: | `pkg/router/errors.go` | JWTSigningError and other error types |\n484: | `pkg/router/config.go` | IdentityNamespace configuration |\n485: \n486: ---\n487: \n488: ## References\n489: \n490: - [AR-009](changes/AR-009/design.md) — Router HTTP Reverse Proxy Core\n491: - [AR-010](changes/AR-010/design.md) — Router Session Management\n492: - [Session Routing Design](../../session-routing/design.md) — Router design overview\n493: - [Client-Go Library](../../deployment/client-go.md) — Kubernetes client usage\n494: - [JWT Specification](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519) — RFC 7519\n495: - [JWS Specification](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7515) — RFC 7515 (RS256)\n496: - [Delta Specification](delta-spec.md) — Detailed requirements and scenarios\n497: \n498: ---\n499: \n500: *AR-011 — Module: pkg/router — Language: Go — Size: M*\n\n(End of file - total 500 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"<base64-encoded PKIX data>\n-----END PUBLIC KEY-----\n```\n\n### Kubernetes Secret Structure\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Secret\nmetadata:\n  name: picod-router-identity\n  namespace: <AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE>\n  labels:\n    app: agentcube\n    component: router\ntype: Opaque\ndata:\n  private.pem: <base64-encoded PKCS#1 PEM>\n  public.pem: <base64-encoded PKIX PEM>\n```","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-011/design.md","time":{"start":1775862583176,"end":1775862583192}}}}
