{"type":"text","timestamp":1775862627715,"sessionID":"ses_2865b0a75ffepxYCm60X9v5r8p","part":{"id":"prt_d79a8e295001KPUqM7wZ4C1v8k","messageID":"msg_d79a88fce001xP3l8oE05dM1CK","sessionID":"ses_2865b0a75ffepxYCm60X9v5r8p","type":"text","text":"I've successfully written the `design.md` file for AR-011 (Router JWT Authentication and Issuance). The document includes:\n\n**Completed sections:**\n\n1. **Architecture** - High-level design with ASCII diagrams showing:\n   - JWT Manager component interactions\n   - Key persistence flow\n   - Token generation flow\n\n2. **Data Structures** - JWTManager struct, constants (`rsaKeySize`, `jwtExpiration`, etc.), and package variables (`IdentityNamespace`)\n\n3. **API Contracts** - All method signatures with behaviors:\n   - `NewJWTManager()` - RSA key generation\n   - `GenerateToken(claims)` - Token creation with RS256 signing\n   - `GetPublicKeyPEM()` / `GetPrivateKeyPEM()` - PEM encoding\n   - `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret()` - Kubernetes Secret persistence\n\n4. **Error Handling** - Error types (`JWTSigningError`) and error scenarios table\n\n5. **Testing Strategy** - Unit tests and integration tests with coverage targets (80% min, 90% target)\n\n6. **Dependencies** - Direct dependencies (jwt/v5, client-go) and standard library packages\n\n7. **Configuration** - Environment variable (`AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE`)\n\n8. **Implementation Details** - RSA key generation, token claims structure, PEM encoding formats, Kubernetes Secret structure, RS256 algorithm details\n\n9. **Security Considerations** - Key management, token security, and RBAC requirements\n\n10. **Migration Notes** - Adding JWT support and downstream changes\n\n11. **File Index** - Files involved (`jwt.go`, `errors.go`, `config.go`)\n\n12. **References** - Links to related documents (AR-009, AR-010, session-routing design, client-go, RFC specifications)\n\nThe document is **500 lines** and provides comprehensive technical implementation details for the JWT authentication component in `pkg/router`.","time":{"start":1775862627712,"end":1775862627712}}}
